description: This file contains Jest test cases for testing performance metrics functionalities such as feature flags, experiments, counters, marks, and measures in the performance metrics module.

methods.name: featureEnabled
methods.description: Checks if a specific feature flag is enabled.

methods.name: experiments
methods.description: Reads and returns whether experiments are enabled.

methods.name: counter
methods.description: Increments and returns a counter for a specific metric.

methods.name: mark
methods.description: Marks a specific point in performance measurement.

methods.name: measure
methods.description: Measures the duration between two points.
